title: KISS - Live at Detroit, MI 5/18/1990 PROSHOT
description:
Great concert by KISS! I think this is the Ultimate Edition 5.1, but Im not sure... quality is excellent.

Date: 90-05-18
Venue: Palace of Auburn Hills

Recording: PRO
Quality: 9(+)
Menu: YES
Extras: None
Comments: Ultimate Edition 5.1. No difference in picture quality compared to the Mike Edwards or Sully versions. Audio doesn't really make that much of a difference either except that it is 5.1 and a little more balanced.
